 But yes, on the 10th day of the month is really special.

00:22:58.520 --> 00:23:02.520
 And of course, this is with the Tibetan calendar, a lunar calendar.

00:23:02.520 --> 00:23:05.520
 So again, on this outer level,

00:23:05.520 --> 00:23:10.520
 the calendar is in sync with the cycles of the outer world,

00:23:10.520 --> 00:23:13.520
 the sun and the moon.

00:23:13.520 --> 00:23:17.520
 So the 10th day of the waxing moon is a special day.

00:23:17.520 --> 00:23:20.520
 We usually do practice on Guru Padmasambhala.

00:23:20.520 --> 00:23:23.520
 And as you all know, the 25th day of the month,

00:23:23.520 --> 00:23:26.520
 or which is the 10th day of the waning moon,

00:23:26.520 --> 00:23:31.520
 we do special practices of the dakini, wisdom dakini,

00:23:31.520 --> 00:23:33.520
 which is also a guru yoga practice.

00:23:33.520 --> 00:23:37.520
 But to get to the 10th day practice,

00:23:37.520 --> 00:23:40.520
 the 10th day is just special in that sense.

00:23:40.520 --> 00:23:46.520
 Again, in our teachings, we're given so many tools

00:23:46.520 --> 00:23:50.520
 for kind of connecting with our bodhicitta

00:23:50.520 --> 00:23:52.520
 and making our aspirations,

00:23:52.520 --> 00:23:55.520
 doing our practice on the rhythms of the nature,

00:23:55.520 --> 00:24:01.520
 kind of riding those waves to kind of make the benefits more powerful.

00:24:01.520 --> 00:24:09.520
 And so the waxing moon time is especially increasing time.

00:24:09.520 --> 00:24:13.520
 And especially from the kind of quarter moon to the full moon

00:24:13.520 --> 00:24:16.520
 is especially prime time.

00:24:16.520 --> 00:24:19.520
 And the 10th day is especially beautiful.

00:24:19.520 --> 00:24:25.520
 Many of Guru Padmasambhala's activities happened on the 10th day.

00:24:25.520 --> 00:24:28.520
 And Guru Padmasambhala himself said,

00:24:28.520 --> 00:24:32.520
 especially when he had spent all these years in Tibet

00:24:32.520 --> 00:24:36.520
 and when the king and the retinues went up to the mountain pass

00:24:36.520 --> 00:24:39.520
 and Guru Padmasambhala was about to depart,

00:24:39.520 --> 00:24:43.520
 he gave those instructions in different texts

00:24:43.520 --> 00:24:49.520
 for those devoted disciples who arise at dawn

00:24:49.520 --> 00:24:52.520
 and practice on me on the 10th day.

00:24:52.520 --> 00:24:56.520
 I'm there with all the sunbeams, all the moonbeams

00:24:56.520 --> 00:25:02.520
 in all of the rainbow light appearing in the sky

00:25:02.520 --> 00:25:05.520
 and all the droplets in the rainbow kind of.

00:25:05.520 --> 00:25:09.520
 My blessings are there, especially on the 10th day.

00:25:09.520 --> 00:25:14.520
 So the 10th day is particularly, again, a very powerful day

00:25:14.520 --> 00:25:17.520
 to reconnect with Guru Padmasambhala.

00:25:17.520 --> 00:25:22.520
 And then we also know we have the Ganachakra ceremony

00:25:22.520 --> 00:25:28.520
 or the Sok ceremony as part of the 10th day practices.

00:25:28.520 --> 00:25:31.520
 And of course, if we don't have the opportunity

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:33.520
 and we're by ourselves, we do.

00:25:33.520 --> 00:25:38.520
 But then especially, it's especially known as renowned,

00:25:38.520 --> 00:25:43.520
 such a strong practice for all these aspects we have.

00:25:43.520 --> 00:25:54.520
 The Sok ceremony means Sok, means to assemble, the assembly.

00:25:54.520 --> 00:26:00.520
 So who's assembled? All the Sangha is assembled.

00:26:00.520 --> 00:26:04.520
 And we're meditating on the whole assembly

00:26:04.520 --> 00:26:08.520
 of the mandala of the Guru.

00:26:08.520 --> 00:26:12.520
 And we're assembling all beautiful merit,

00:26:12.520 --> 00:26:16.520
 making feast offering and offerings.

00:26:16.520 --> 00:26:19.520
 So on all those aspects, all the good qualities

00:26:19.520 --> 00:26:22.520
 are assembled and connected and offered.

00:26:22.520 --> 00:26:26.520
 So we're generating merit in offering.

00:26:26.520 --> 00:26:30.520
 But also, it's a very powerful time, again, to do what?

00:26:30.520 --> 00:26:36.520
 Purify our obscurations, any mistakes we've made,

00:26:36.520 --> 00:26:38.520
 any way we become aware,

00:26:38.520 --> 00:26:42.520
 we've perpetuated trouble for ourselves and others,

00:26:42.520 --> 00:26:45.520
 recognizing that, getting up, purifying,

00:26:45.520 --> 00:26:48.520
 connecting with our intention.

00:26:48.520 --> 00:26:54.520
 So generating merit, purifying, and receiving blessings.

00:26:54.520 --> 00:26:59.520
 We do, again, the swiftly penetrating blessings of the Guru Yoga.

