 So in there, every 10th day, in the lunar calendar,

00:27:40.520 --> 00:27:45.520
 there's 12 months, sometimes more, where it's doubled.

00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:49.520
 So the 10th day of every moon

00:27:49.520 --> 00:27:53.520
 is a way of connecting with this one particular activity

00:27:53.520 --> 00:27:55.520
 of Guru Padmasambhava.

00:27:55.520 --> 00:27:58.520
